settings.faq_question: How can I place an order?
settings.faq_description: To place an order, simply browse our products, select the items you want, and click "Add to Cart." Follow the checkout process to provide your shipping details and payment information.

settings.faq_question: Can I modify or cancel my order after it's placed?Aurchase.
settings.faq_description: Unfortunately, once an order is confirmed, it cannot be modified or canceled. Please double-check your order before completing the purchase.
